    <section id="jjk" class="anime-section">
        <div class="anime-content">
            <h2>Jujutsu Kaisen</h2>
            <img class="anime-thumbnail" src="https://images5.alphacoders.com/114/1141137.jpg" alt="Yuji Itadori">
            <p>Join Yuji Itadori on his journey to battle curses with the power of Jujutsu sorcery.</p>
            <h3>Main Character: Yuji Itadori</h3>
            <p>Yuji Itadori is an energetic and kind-hearted teenager who becomes the central character of *Jujutsu Kaisen*. After swallowing a cursed object — the finger of a powerful curse named Ryomen Sukuna — Yuji gains immense strength and cursed energy. He decides to join Jujutsu High to help protect people from curses, all while trying to find a way to rid himself of Sukuna's influence. Yuji is driven by his desire to save others, despite the overwhelming odds stacked against him.</p>
        </div>
    </section>    

    <section id="demon-slayer" class="anime-section">
        <div class="anime-content">
            <h2>Demon Slayer</h2>
            <img class="anime-thumbnail" src="https://wallpapers.com/images/hd/intense-tanjiro-kamado-with-demon-slayer-logo-3ztspr616hw9vnkg.jpg" alt="Tanjiro Kamado">
            <p>Follow Tanjiro Kamado as he fights demons with his swordsmanship.</p>
            <h3>Main Character: Tanjiro Kamado</h3>
            <p>Tanjiro Kamado is a determined and compassionate boy whose life changes when his family is slaughtered by demons, and his younger sister, Nezuko, is transformed into one. After witnessing the horrors caused by demons, Tanjiro becomes a Demon Slayer to find a cure for Nezuko and avenge his family. Despite the grim nature of his task, Tanjiro maintains his kindness, humility, and relentless pursuit of justice, making him a beloved and admirable protagonist.</p>
        </div>
    </section>    

